Package org.pikater.shared.database.views.tableview.batches

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BatchTableDBRow  
    BatchTableDBView
    A generic view for tables displaying information on batches (experiments).
    BatchTableDBViewAll
    A view displaying all batches (admin mode).
    BatchTableDBViewUser
    A view displaying all experiments for the given user.
    BatchTableDBViewUserMin  
    BatchTableDBViewUserSaved
    A view displaying all saved (not scheduled) experiments for the given user.
    BatchTableDBViewUserScheduled
    A view displaying all scheduled (whether waiting, started or finished) experiments for the given user.
